import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <footer className='footer'>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col lg='4' md='4' sm='6'></Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
